16:56.520 --> 16:57.720
[both chuckle]

17:00.480 --> 17:01.640
I miss her so much.

17:02.920 --> 17:04.400
I feel sad all the time.

17:06.080 --> 17:07.400
I'm not the person I was.

17:08.520 --> 17:10.240
Lisa dying, I just... It's like...

17:11.560 --> 17:14.680
I lost most of me, and all the good stuff,
all the happiness...

17:15.280 --> 17:16.480
any joy in anything...

17:19.760 --> 17:21.600
