you know,

17:25.720 --> 17:27.760
like I'm getting on with it,
I'm snarky now and again,

17:27.840 --> 17:30.120
and that this is a lapse,
but it's not.

17:30.800 --> 17:32.240
This is me all the time now.

17:34.200 --> 17:36.360
Everything else is the front, you know?

17:37.160 --> 17:38.520
