18:27.640 --> 18:29.080
[sobs, sighs]

18:34.800 --> 18:35.960
[Tony sobs gently]

18:39.320 --> 18:40.400
[Lisa] <i>Be strong.</i>

18:41.320 --> 18:43.880
<i>Everybody's struggling.</i>
<i>It's not always their fault.</i>

18:45.640 --> 18:48.200
<i>There's a porter here</i>
<i>with a bit of a BO problem.</i>

18:49.200 --> 18:52.720
<i>I'm quite glad you haven't bumped</i>
<i>into him, to be honest. He stinks.</i>

18:52.800 --> 18:53.800
