18:53.880 --> 18:55.000
<i>And do you know why?</i>

18:56.040 --> 18:58.600
<i>'Cause he's working twice as hard</i>
<i>as everyone else.</i>

18:58.680 --> 19:01.440
<i>He's always running around doing stuff</i>
<i>for other people.</i>

19:01.520 --> 19:02.680
<i>He's got no idea.</i>

19:03.880 --> 19:07.120
<i>And I was going to say something,</i>
<i>but do you know what came out?</i>

19:07.960 --> 19:09.640
<i>"Thank you for working so hard."</i>

19:10.560 --> 19:11.800
<i>And he nearly cried.</i>

19:13.400 --> 19:16.560
[sighs] <i>Just tell people</i>
<i>you appreciate 'em now and then, yeah?</i>

19:33.080 --> 19:35.760
-[Tony] Hi, sorry. Um...
-Oh, hello.

19:35.840 --> 19:37.240
-Can I...? Um...
-Yeah.

19:37.640 --> 19:40.560
-Is it Tony?
-Yeah. Hi. Um...

19:42.080 --> 19:43.360
Has anyone asked you...

19:43.840 --> 19:46.600
