from selling it?

20:00.880 --> 20:01.880
Half a million.

20:04.040 --> 20:05.600
Right... Yeah.

20:07.440 --> 20:08.440
That's a lot.

20:08.760 --> 20:09.600
Mm.

20:11.080 --> 20:12.560
What will you do with that?

20:14.760 --> 20:15.800
New car, maybe.

20:17.720 --> 20:19.680
Ah... I dunno, um...

20:20.920 --> 20:22.000
Potter around a bit.

20:23.320 --> 20:25.440
No, it's just that, you know, if, um...

20:26.120 --> 20:29.040
if I don't cash in my chips soon,
you know, none of my...

20:29.560 --> 20:31.440
I might kick the bucket,
then it'd be too late.

20:32.560 --> 20:35.640
I mean, it's not as if I need anything
as such, it's, uh...

20:36.240 --> 20:37.600
