22:06.960 --> 22:09.240
<i>-♪ Isn't it rich? ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Isn't it... rich! ♪</i>

22:09.320 --> 22:12.080
-♪ <i>Are... ♪</i>
<i>-♪ Aren't we a pair? ♪</i>

