22:35.360 --> 22:36.960
You can do it without the words.

22:37.040 --> 22:38.280
-Thanks, Ken.
-Just the dance.

22:38.360 --> 22:39.840
-Is that what you want to do?
-Yeah.

22:39.920 --> 22:42.880
