22:44.760 --> 22:46.800
-Thanks, Ken.
-This is why we do it. It's all right.

22:46.880 --> 22:49.040
Hey, have I told you
about my sister's anus yet?

22:49.440 --> 22:51.600
-Uh... I don't think so.
